snippet.title: Diana and Roma English Alphabet with Surprise Eggs | ABC
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma name the Letters of the English Alphabet and find a Surprise Egg under each letter. Have fun learning the ABC with Diana and Roma!
Thanks for watching!
